text = "A [b]slug[/b] is the URL-friendly identifier for your project on itch.io.

[b][color=#6bcfff]Example[/color][/b]

Project name: \"My Awesome Game\"
Slug: [code]my-awesome-game[/code]
URL: [code]https://username.itch.io/my-awesome-game[/code]

[b][color=#6bcfff]Slug Characteristics[/color][/b]

  - Set when you create your project on itch.io
  - Lowercase letters and hyphens only
  - URL-friendly (no spaces or special characters)
  - Used in all API calls and butler uploads

[b][color=#6bcfff]How It's Used[/color][/b]

Butler uses the slug in the upload path:
  [code]profile/project:channel[/code]

Example: [code]johndoe/my-awesome-game:windows[/code]

[b][color=#ffcc66]Finding Your Slug[/color][/b]

Look at your project's URL on itch.io:
  [code]https://username.itch.io/your-slug-here[/code]"
